Margaret Early https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Early 0 Margaret Early (December 25, 1919 – November 29, 2000) was an American film actress who was active in Hollywood during the 1930s and 1940s. She is best remembered for her endearing Southern charm.
